abstracts.swe: Skriv in din svenska sammanfattning eller abstrakt här!
abstracts.eng: \engExpl {Enter your abstract here and remove this line!} An abstract is (typically) about 250 and 350 words (1/2 A4-page) with the following components: \par \begin {itemize} \item What is the topic area? (optional) Introduces the subject area for the project. \item Short problem statement \item Why was this problem worth a third-cycle thesis? (\ie why is the problem both significant and of a suitable degree of difficulty for your intended degree? Why has no one else solved it yet?) \item How did you solve the problem? What was your method/insight? \item Results/Conclusions/Consequences/Impact: What are your key results/\linebreak [4]conclusions? What will others do based on your results? What can be done now that you have finished - that could not be done before your thesis project was completed? \end {itemize} \par
